  https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

License documented per-file via headers in every .tex source file in
this directory, which read (typical):

  %By Kevin Cheung
  %The book is licensed under the
  %Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International License.
  %This file has been modified by Robert Hildebrand 2020.
  %CC BY SA 4.0 licence still applies.

The directory also contains the CC BY-SA badge image at images/by-sa.png.
The upstream GitHub repository does not include a standalone LICENSE file;
the per-file headers are definitive.

The content has been adapted by Robert Hildebrand for inclusion in
"Mathematical Programming and Operations Research," which is licensed
under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0 International
(CC BY-SA 4.0).

CC BY-SA 4.0 source content is directly compatible with CC BY-SA 4.0
adaptation; no license version transition is needed.
